<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <title>OX</title>
        <meta name="description" content="oxQuiz">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
		<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous" />

        <style>
           body{ background-image : url('/cloud.jpg');
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-position: center;
                background-size: cover; } 

            @font-face { font-family: 'font'; src: url('https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/projectnoonnu/noonfonts_nine_@1.1/BBTreeGB.woff') format('woff'); font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; }
            h6 {
				font-family: 'font', sans-serif;
				font-size: 30px;
			}
            h8 {
				font-family: 'font', sans-serif;
				font-size: 15px;
			}
            </style>
    </head>

	<body>

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm" onClick='window.close()' style="float: right;">닫기</button>

        </br>

        <h6 style = "text-align:center;"><b>OX 퀴즈를 풀어라!!</b></h6>

        </br>
        
        <h7><I>아래 문제를 잘 읽고 옳은 문제의 번호를 아래에 작성해 제출해 주세요!</I></h7>

        <br></br>

        <div class="btn-group" role="group" aria-label="Basic mixed styles example">
            <table class="table">
                <tbody>
                <% for (var i = 0; i < posts.length; i++){ %>
                  <tr>
                    <th scope="row"><%= i+1 %></th>
                    <td><h8><b><%= posts[i].question %></b></h8></td>
                  </tr>
                  <% } %>
                </tbody>
              </table>
        </div>

        <form action="/ox" method="post">
            <div class="input-group input-group-sm mb-3">
                <p><I>올바른 답을 말한 문제 번호를 예시와 같은 형식으로 써 주세요 (만약 1, 2, 5번이 맞다면 <b>125</b>)</I></p>
                <span class="input-group-text" id="inputGroup-sizing-sm">Answer</span>
                <input type="text" name="ans" class="form-control" aria-label="Sizing example input" aria-describedby="inputGroup-sizing-sm">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark">제출</button>
            </div>
        </form>

	</body>
</html>